snippet.title: Telebbit | Release Date Trailer
snippet.description:
The rabbit has commenced its revenge on humanity! 2D precision platformer where teleportation is key.
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2504250/Telebbit/

Take the teleporter and escape the lab!
A simple device, it teleports the user to the location at which it's fired, but the possibilities become endless when combined with in-stage gimmicks! At the end of each stage, a boss stands ready to fight.

-Speedy platformer with unique teleportation mechanics
-Test your perseverance, effort and imagination with highly challenging stages
-Eight charming underground worlds to explore and wreak havoc in
-Clean and minimalist pixel art punctuated by striking, lurid colors
-Speedrun mode available for time attack play

Title: Telebbit
Genre: Platformer
Platform: PC(Steam)・Nintendo Switch・PlayStation 5・Xbox Series X|S
Developer: IKINAGAMES 
Publisher: HYPER REAL
Release: October 24, 2024
Price: TBA
